channel.title: (delta) help, im baffled! npcs dont load!
channel.description: hello, i was just beginning a new project to transform a blank allstar source into a good decent server, but now when i log in there are no npcs. i did not delete anything from autospawn.cfg, and i have not touched npc.java or npchandler.java. the only thing i have done recently is make a new system for the wilderness, and try and make a shitty anti null thing. i wish there was an error from compiling or from the server, but there isn't, so i have absolutely no clue what is causing this. if you think you know please tell me so i can fix it! thanks a lot, otherwise i might scratch this whole damn project.... or have to restart... :eek: :mad:
